{"about_the_game":"\u25c6 Knead the dough. Roll out the dough. Every detail, from the stretching and rising of dough to the splashing of sauces and melting of cheese, is finely crafted.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/gif3_fix.gif?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Here is your fully equipped kitchen. Customize your cozy apartment to reflect your unique style and taste. It's your safe space to relax and enjoy while learning to make delicious pizza.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/Screenshot14.png?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 The game boasts highly realistic object physics, enabling interaction with ingredients and kitchen tools just as in real life.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/gif4_1.gif?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Embark on your culinary journey and level up your character\u2019s skills and perks. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/Screenshot9_2.png?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Cut any ingredients into pieces of any size at different angles. We have implemented the cutting to be as realistic as possible.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/gif11.gif?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 Choose ingredients to your taste or according to real-life recipes.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2554880/extras/Screenshot17.png?t=1731054489\" /><br><br>\u25c6 The cooking mechanics are meticulously designed, challenging you to master techniques like kneading, slicing, and baking to create the perfect pizza.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass